  "original_title": "\u0b8e\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf \u201c\u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe \u0b95\u0bcb \u0b95\u0bae\u201d \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Attack on the Empilipitian \u201cKota Ko Kama\u201d.",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Unidentified persons have attacked the protest site of Kalimugattidal \"Kota Ko Kama\" branch located in Embilipitiya area.",
        "No one was injured during the attack but damage was done to the goods and belongings."
      ],
